item.title: Moshel School
item.description: Overview # ß· This article is about a location in Vekllei The Moshel Street State School, also the Moshel School or Lola 6th, is a Central School in the borough of Lola. It is the second-largest school in Lola, and offers schooling between Prep and Year 12. It is also Tzipora’s school, and is where she completes her secondary schooling upon her arrival in Vekllei. As a Central School, Moshel St occupies a large grounds that are well-equipped with facilities, including a dining hall, multipurpose gymnasium, photographic, photonic computing, and chemical laboratories, and a large school library.
